OL,4,Cson in special care baby unit
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,7,Fthat some may find distressing.
OL,9,FA father has been found guilty of
OL,10,Fkilling his premature son, who was
OL,11,Fbeing cared for in a special care baby
OL,12,Funit.
OL,14,FDaniel Gunter, 27, inflicted
OL,15,F"catastrophic injuries" to the head,
OL,16,Fneck, legs and jaw of two-week-old
OL,17,FBrendon Staddon while on the ward at
OL,18,Fthe Yeovil District Hospital, in
OL,19,FSomerset, on 5 March last year.
