OL,6,FBristol Crown Court heard that after
OL,7,Finflicting the fatal injuries which
OL,8,Fleft his son's head "crushed", Gunter
OL,9,Fwalked out of the hospital for a
OL,10,Fcigarette, leaving nurses desperately
OL,11,Fattempting to resuscitate him.
OL,13,FGunter denied harming him, but was
OL,14,Fconvicted of murder following a three-
OL,15,Fweek trial.
