OL,6,FHis former partner, Sophie Staddon,
OL,7,F23, was cleared of a lesser charge of
OL,8,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,9,Fchild.
OL,11,FThe jury previously found Staddon not
OL,12,Fguilty of murder and cleared Gunter of
OL,13,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,14,Fchild on the direction of the trial
OL,15,Fjudge, Mr Justice Swift.
OL,17,FRemanding Gunter into custody, the
OL,18,Fjudge told him: "Daniel Gunter you
OL,19,Fhave been found guilty of murder. You
OL,20,Fwill be remanded into custody pending
OL,21,Fthe sentencing hearing.
