OL,6,F"Sophie Staddon you have been
OL,7,Facquitted by the jury. Your bail will
OL,8,Fno longer be necessary and you are
OL,9,Ffree to go."
OL,11,FDuring the trial, jurors heard that
OL,12,Fnurses discovered Brendon's injuries
OL,13,Fafter Staddon told nurses her son was
OL,14,Fcold and asked them to check on him.
OL,16,FCharles Row KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,17,F"Staff found him lying in his cot with
OL,18,Fhis baby grow open. They immediately
OL,19,Fsaw that he wasn't just cold but that
OL,20,Fhe had suffered catastrophic injuries."
