OL,6,FThe baby, who was born at 33 weeks'
OL,7,Fgestation and weighed 1.83kg at birth,
OL,8,Fwas carried to the resuscitation area
OL,9,Fbut did not respond to treatment and
OL,10,Fdied at 4.59am.
OL,12,F'Injuries were like nothing I've seen
OL,13,Fbefore', says detective
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Nadine
OL,16,FPartridge, of Avon and Somerset
OL,17,FPolice, described Gunter's actions as
OL,18,F"evil".
