OL,6,F"The extent of the injuries were like
OL,7,Fnothing I've seen before," she said.
OL,8,F"Brendon's little tiny precious body
OL,9,Fat just two weeks old, there wasn't
OL,10,Fany part of him that wasn't harmed."
OL,12,FThe jury heard Gunter and Staddon were
OL,13,Farrested by the police while smoking
OL,14,Foutside.
OL,16,FMr Row said that before Brendon died,
OL,17,Fsocial services and Gunter's family
OL,18,Fwere worried about the "lack of
OL,19,Femotional warmth" the couple showed
OL,20,Ftheir child.
