OL,6,FGunter and Sophie Staddon make phone
OL,7,Fcalls and vape while medics try to
OL,8,Fsave baby Brendon's life
OL,10,FWhile in hospital, Gunter repeatedly
OL,11,Fignored the advice of nurses, taking
OL,12,FBrendon out of the incubator without
OL,13,Fasking, overstimulating the child to
OL,14,Fthe point of causing him distress and
OL,15,Fremoving his nasal gastric tube.
OL,17,FFamily members had witnessed Gunter
OL,18,Fshouting and getting angry at Brendon
OL,19,Fwhile visiting them in hospital and
OL,20,Fwould handle him roughly.
