OL,6,FThe court also heard the pair had an
OL,7,Fon-off relationship, with allegations
OL,8,Fthat he was "violent" towards her on
OL,9,Foccasion.
OL,11,FIn January 2024, a social worker
OL,12,Fvisited the couple and told them that
OL,13,Fauthorities were planning to remove
OL,14,Fthe baby from their care when he was
OL,15,Fborn.
