OL,6,FMr Row said: "The authorities were
OL,7,Fconcerned about many things, including
OL,8,Ftheir precarious housing situation,
OL,9,Fthe way Mr Gunter appeared to control
OL,10,FMs Staddon and her finances, Ms
OL,11,FStaddon's physical and mental health
OL,12,Fand their lack of engagement."
OL,14,F"Brendon was deemed to be at risk of
OL,15,Fneglect, not physical harm," said Det
OL,16,FCh Insp Partridge.
